{"tid":1978563,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 23條立法聯署已經突破200萬人簽！！","createTime":"2020-04-18T19:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T17:20:40.000Z","uid":179108,"like":26,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"86db1241b3aef3bbcc544e9704c140fc5f178d17","tid":1978563,"uid":179108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:52:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Sorry呃左你地入黎</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rw7LoT8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRw7LoT8.png&h=cc589ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但已經突破左</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">190萬</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">人簽</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁多位香港人你地醒未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對家連聯署都多人過我地</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMSWvzq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMSWvzq.png&h=3ebcc196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足建立嘅香港獨立聯署得3萬幾人簽<br />\n點解你地連簽個名都咁難<br />\n係咪要求你地先肯去做？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聯署喺4月22號就到期 仲有最後4日時間<br />\n未簽嘅快撚啲去簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好齋望望完就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsupport-hong-kong-independence&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e28f4091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-i